OL,5, A Plaid Cymru councillor who dubbed two
OL,6, colleagues "outsiders" has been        
OL,7, suspended after telling them: "Wales is
OL,8, for Welsh people."                     
OL,10,FTerry Davies was found to have used    
OL,11,Fdiscriminatory language by             
OL,12,FCarmarthenshire council's standards    
OL,13,Fcommittee against fellow councillors   
OL,14,FAndre McPherson and Suzy Curry.        
OL,16,FIt also decided he probably swore at Mr
OL,17,FMcPherson outside a playground.        
OL,19,FThe ombudsman previously said Mr Davies
OL,20,Fcalled the Labour members "outsiders". 
